Merge all chapter hierarchies from the 3rd outline level (HTML only).

!begin_xlist [(!TYPEPOSITION)]

!item [(!TYPEPOSITION)] (!COMMAND), (!PREAMBLE)

!item [(!SYNTAX)] (!T)!/html_merge_subsubnodes(!t)

!item [(!DESCRIPTION)]
If you use this switch inside the UDO source preamble, all chapter hierarchies from the 3rd outline level will be combined into one single HTML file.

